{"tid":1465533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與其話今次點樣搞臭形象，不如諗下點帶返好個風向仲好過啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:01.000Z","uid":201601,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e512e06178b53b2a3aeb97e615f71459825c84ad","tid":1465533,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:08:16.000Z","msg":"有啲話今次搞到遊客delay嗰啲etc<br />\n話咩外國人冇義務頂我地不合作運動搞出嘅大頭佛，呢個我都明，但依家非常時期，可唔可以顧返香港人嘅五大訴求先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家都未搞掂香港人自己嘅問題，就係度擔心點樣煩到外國人，不如搞清楚主次先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武又話太暴力，搞不合作又話阻到其他人<br />\n淨係識屌自己友，不如諗下點補鑊先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當我地比人屌嘅話，比佢地睇番共匪黑警班賤種點對示威者仲好過啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n話破壞咗香港示威者咩和平理性嘅形象嘅話，咁就比佢睇返警黑點樣合作；睇下警犬對住老人細路照話tg放題；睇返個絲打點比人射爆面囉<br />\n<br />\n總之就spin到我地呢班和平理性嘅示威者點樣比人迫到要搞埋其他人，而唔係係度屌屌屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真，外國罷工咪一樣照搞到其他人，但佢地咪一樣理西得你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能我呢個point唔夠concrete，但我覺得將個責任推番班對家嗰邊條橋應該work，再唔係就大家一齊諗辦法搞搞佢，而唔係一味批評<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要記住勿分化、勿捉鬼、不篤灰、不抹黑、不割蓆</span></span><br />\n<br />\nsor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de50071f341a07ad69f79a47c9bbb3c6b5b8e5d9","tid":1465533,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:08:20.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"41e9921a2bf092537ffa289358537ab306ea2bfe","tid":1465533,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:09:00.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9491c9f4ce26e08547122a8fb657f5385a8ec0c4","tid":1465533,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:09:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【入黎】我正式宣佈，今日輸撚咗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464718</a>"},{"pid":"34ccb3e6592abede1fd6bb4d08a057f0cf41f36d","tid":1465533,"uid":40742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:09:39.000Z","msg":"重點帶風向啦！"},{"pid":"30aadf826bd6da498b726787f3d689377bfb88e8","tid":1465533,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edbc8a8390eb5da233175ae939fb0c671b4116ce","tid":1465533,"uid":305546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"我地仲有好多持唔同態度既人<br />\n我唔知現場有無鬼 但我地要撐住<br />\n真正的不割席系和理非要繼續發聲<br />\n一齊諗諗經此一役 我地要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">檢討策略 救返民意!</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好講負皮說話!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e95b13ec0142768d22ef27cb8444f615bede1fda","tid":1465533,"uid":305546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"c1790e0f9342c895fcb3bd0b12ae8cfb7f0f61b3","tid":1465533,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:10:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: r